# USER STORIES

## MVP
- As a user, I would like to see a greeting page with the persons name so that users can know what information to expect.
- As a user, I want to see a "about me" so that I can know more about the person
- As a user, I want to be able to access the resume so that it could be shared with employers
- As a user, I want a way to interact and see the projects so that it could be used as reference
- As a user, I want to access the website from any platform so that it could be shared with anyone



## Bronze
- A way to get a user's information if they want to contact me
-




## Silver
- Quiz about myself



## Gold
- maybe some game like black jack to gamble earned points from quiz
